reviewText: I bought this under the impression there were six tales, but there were only 5 , the last tale, the loyal dog was not on the dvds, the translation to  English was poorly done, many misspelled words, wrong usuage of our vocabulary and many unnescessary curse words that really took away from the beauty and sincercity of the tales, which were quite beautiful
I love these great Chinese movies. There is always some sort of strange or tragic twist in these. The set are just gorgeous.
